What you need to know:

Rosaline Guyo Gollo was six years old when she was forced to undergo Female Genital Mutilation.On the fateful day, her relatives took her and her then eight-year-old elder sister from school.She developed bleeding complications after the cut, that lasted for about a month. Unknown to her, she would, six years later, endure a more excruciating procedure.Ms Gollo broke into tears on learning, years later, that she could never have children the normal way due to the infibulations.